data.text: PAUL NGUYEN 38, of Oakland, CA, passed away August 25, 2003. Born February 10, 1965 in Saigon, Vietnam to Robert and Nhung Nguyen. Survived by his wife, Julie Nguyen, son, Steven Nguyen, daughters, Jennifer and Stephanie Nguyen all of Hayward, CA. Paul married Julie Nguyen on April 11, 1987 in Hayward, CA and was employed as a Manager at ANG Newspapers. Visitation August 27, 2003, 2 – 8 p.m. at Mission Funeral Home. A Rosary to be held August 28, 2003, 4 – 8 p.m. at Mission Funeral Home. Service to be held August 29, 2003, 10:30 a.m. at All Saints, Hayward, CA. Donations to The Nguyen Family, appreciated. MISSION FUNERAL HOME 510-881-9192
